<section class="ui two column grid segment">
	<div class="ui row">
		<div class="ui column">
			<h2 class="ui header">Welcome to the Playlist App, {{fullname}}!</h2>
			<p>With this app, you can track your sim racing championships.</p>
			<p>When you complete a race from a championship, first you will need to make championship, then inside you
				will need to enter in a race along with the number of the race in championship (might not always count up sequentially
